{
  "texts": [
    "Another study used an attention mechanism enhanced LSTM with residual architecture to predict protein-protein interaction residue pairs.",
    "The model achieved high accuracy and outperformed other state-ofthe-art models [105].",
    "Lastly, a DL framework called MusiteDeep was proposed for phosphorylation site prediction.",
    "The model performed well in kinase-specific prediction tasks and achieved high accuracy.",
    "These studies demonstrate the potential of DL in various bioinformatics applications, including miRNA-target prediction, protein sequence classification, protein-protein interaction prediction, and phosphorylation site prediction."
  ]
}